{"tid":1430634,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住，今晚變左Party","createTime":"2019-08-07T19:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T02:04:10.000Z","uid":170652,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"41c8f38292d008e5f5aa9f3ad13562aed691f188","tid":1430634,"uid":170652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:32:56.000Z","msg":"對唔住今晚本身一個抗爭事情變左一個party<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但多謝呢一晚<br />\n令我過左我成個暑假最開心嘅一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我每日都過得好嬲同好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家幾乎每日都有義士被捕同俾狗亂告<br />\n個垃圾政府又唔知係到做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至有諗過事情再咁走落去一死好似輕鬆啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝今晚尖咀嘅雷射革命<br />\n令我有返啲生存嘅動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人真係好可愛<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我真係好愛香港同埋你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n最後<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人加油<br />\n我地未達到五大訴求前<br />\n不撤不散<br />\n仲有唔好講大大力錫春袋<br />\n含埋<br />\n放核彈<br />\n我都唔撚會割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位戰場上再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"92234b4f793466569c761ce715ca89b303384538","tid":1430634,"uid":156527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:33:55.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"f5d7365eaa953c3759cba52e5507e1e333f053f3","tid":1430634,"uid":58616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7c3eb6e60bdf1df587c235d5eb5796ef44a776","tid":1430634,"uid":194169,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:38:58.000Z","msg":"唔洗講對唔住<br />\n今晚係你應得嘅，係大家應得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e0272d7911e310a24c3c4aa7e0f9caf738dd44","tid":1430634,"uid":170652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c7c3eb6e60bdf1df587c235d5eb5796ef44a776","tid":1430634,"uid":194169,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:38:58.000Z","msg":"唔洗講對唔住<br />\n今晚係你應得嘅，係大家應得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:51:40.000Z","msg":"等一天光曬嘅時候<br />\n我地再搵一日一齊開心過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13804176ef526c41443cd11600a05b19432c07d1","tid":1430634,"uid":140924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T20:03:58.000Z","msg":"唔使對唔住喎，我諗好多人都需要今晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺屋企睇live都覺得個人放鬆咗<br />\n今晚過後再出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ebf417c43873d2081d14ec59fd9d25b0240ac8","